data.description: Charming Brick Beauty!!! This 3 bedroom, 2 bath Ranch Style Brick beauty in the much-desired Shangri-LA Place subdivision with a spacious yard is perfect for outdoor entertainment and activities!!  This cozy home features a sunken living room with wood burning fireplace and a separate dining room while the galley kitchen features a breakfast area and a roomy pantry!!  The sizable primary suite includes a private en-suite bathroom with double closets, while the two additional bedrooms offer plenty of space for guests or a growing family.  Parking is not a problem with the double car garage and paved driveway. This property is a GEM!! Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful brick house your new home!  CALL and schedule your private tour TODAY!!
